  "texts": [
    "These probabilities will shift depending on whatever portion of the molecule the network has seen before.",
    "Attaching an extra model (like RL) as a property optimizer also yields unique compounds.",
    "Each input value impacts the subsequent output value when sequential data are fed into the RNN step by step.",
    ", xt are fed to the RNN as input values, where at every step t, xt is a d-dimensional feature vector.",
    "For instance, if the model gets a group of words as input, then every word wi is shown as a vector xi."
